examples.en: After the storm, the road was covered in deep puddles.
examples.ru: После грозы дорога была покрыта глубокими лужами.

examples.en: I accidentally stepped in a puddle.
He puddles about at a great rate.
Tablecloths were puddled with melted ice-cream.
He was standing in a puddle of water.
She accidentally stepped in a puddle and got her shoes wet.
examples.ru: Она случайно наступила в лужу и промочила обувь.

examples.en: The child leapt across the puddle.
He had fallen asleep, his head resting in a puddle of beer.
examples.ru: Он уснул, головой в пивной луже.

examples.en: He stepped into an ankle-deep puddle of mud.
examples.ru: Он по щиколотку наступил в лужу жидкой грязи.

examples.en: He stepped ankle-deep into a puddle of mud.
examples.ru: Он по щиколотку наступил в лужу жидкой грязи.

examples.en: He fell plumb in the middle of the puddle.
She took a small jump forward to avoid stepping in the puddle.
examples.ru: Он сделал небольшой скачок вперёд, чтобы не наступить в лужу.
